<br>
OK, in doing the research on this spell, it does just over 2K damage in just 1min 48 seconds. Like you said when we were talking about it, on raids where mobs live longer this can be cool. Also think about soloing possibilities. Cast Nife (1648 points in 42 seconds), then Pox, then Nife once more when it fades, and there you have over 5k damage in just about 2 mins. Can't hurt to drop Insidious Decay to debuff disease too.<br>
